You need to talk to the rest of your crew before you
can proceed! There should be five mateys in all!
I'm glad to be away from that jungle!
Now if only there were a way through this cave...
Ahoy son, thank ye fer findin' me in the midst o'
these nasty natives!
I 'ave ne'er seen such injuries on livin' scallywags
afore. By all accounts these poor souls should 'ave
met thar maker a long time ago..
Truthfully I don't know what be keepin' them alive.
Thank ye again, my boy for rescuin' my sorry hide!
Those bony souls be too unnatural for me taste.
Uh? Who are ye? Lost me way? HA!
I 'ave ne'er been lost in me life.
While kickin' these skeletons in their bony rears I
noticed they be equipped with rusted cutlasses.
I don't supposed these skeletons 'ave swabed thar
weapons in twenty years!
I been looking at these skeletons' arms ..err weapons
and it really do seem like they be years old. Being
stuck like this for so long has got to be a fate worse
than death.
I been examinin' some of these here plants I gathered
in the jungle, but I can't place their origin.
They be like nothing else I've ever seen.
